---
title: All-American Chicken & Bacon Jam Tacos  with Cucumber Cos Salad, Herby Mayo & Smoked Cheddar
description: Are you ready to rumble with All-American spiced chicken tacos? Land that knock out with a bacon jam and follow up with a
smooth herby mayo. Take home the best-taco medal by sprinkling over a smokey Cheddar cheese at the end.
